{"metadata":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"pathComponent","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"String","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"externalID":"s:11PopguideSDK9ApiClientC10MiddlewareV13pathComponentSSvp","symbolKind":"property","roleHeading":"Instance Property","modules":[{"name":"PopguideSDK"}],"title":"pathComponent"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/popguide-sdk-ios.PopguideSDK\/documentation\/PopguideSDK","doc:\/\/popguide-sdk-ios.PopguideSDK\/documentation\/PopguideSDK\/ApiClient","doc:\/\/popguide-sdk-ios.PopguideSDK\/documentation\/PopguideSDK\/ApiClient\/Middleware"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"pathComponent","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Examples:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"pathComponent"},{"type":"text","text":" is “user”, the middleware is applied only to requests"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that include “\/user” in their URL path, such as “https:\/\/example.com\/api\/user” or “https:\/\/example.com\/api\/user\/details”."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"pathComponent"},{"type":"text","text":" is “\/v1”, the middleware targets requests with “\/v1” in their path,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"like “https:\/\/example.com\/api\/v1\/products” or “https:\/\/example.com\/api\/v1\/users\/123”."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Using “\/” as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"pathComponent"},{"type":"text","text":" means the middleware applies to every request, regardless of its path."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This is useful for applying global behaviors, such as logging all requests or adding common headers"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to every request made by the application."}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This targeted application makes it possible to layer middleware based on URL structure, enabling","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"fine-grained control over request modification and response handling based on specific endpoints or services."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/popguidesdk\/apiclient\/middleware\/pathcomponent"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Path components are the segments in the URL after the domain, separated by “\/”. For example, in the URL “https:\/\/example.com\/v1\/user”, the path components are “v1” and “user”."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If you specify the path component as “\/”, the middleware will be applied to every API call, regardless of its specific path."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/popguide-sdk-ios.PopguideSDK\/documentation\/PopguideSDK\/ApiClient\/Middleware\/pathComponent"},"references":{"doc://popguide-sdk-ios.PopguideSDK/documentation/PopguideSDK/ApiClient/Middleware/pathComponent":{"title":"pathComponent","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Path components are the segments in the URL after the domain, separated by “\/”. For example, in the URL “https:\/\/example.com\/v1\/user”, the path components are “v1” and “user”."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If you specify the path component as “\/”, the middleware will be applied to every API call, regardless of its specific path."}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"pathComponent","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/popguidesdk\/apiclient\/middleware\/pathcomponent","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/popguide-sdk-ios.PopguideSDK\/documentation\/PopguideSDK\/ApiClient\/Middleware\/pathComponent"},"doc://popguide-sdk-ios.PopguideSDK/documentation/PopguideSDK":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/popguide-sdk-ios.PopguideSDK\/documentation\/PopguideSDK","abstract":[],"role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/popguidesdk","kind":"symbol","title":"PopguideSDK"},"doc://popguide-sdk-ios.PopguideSDK/documentation/PopguideSDK/ApiClient":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/popguide-sdk-ios.PopguideSDK\/documentation\/PopguideSDK\/ApiClient","title":"ApiClient","abstract":[],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"ApiClient"}],"url":"\/documentation\/popguidesdk\/apiclient","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"ApiClient"}]},"doc://popguide-sdk-ios.PopguideSDK/documentation/PopguideSDK/ApiClient/Middleware":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/popguide-sdk-ios.PopguideSDK\/documentation\/PopguideSDK\/ApiClient\/Middleware","title":"ApiClient.Middleware","abstract":[{"text":"Represents a middleware component that can be applied to network requests and responses.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This struct defines a middleware with a unique identifier, target URL path component,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a callback closure to execute, and specifies whether it should be applied before the request is sent"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or after the response is received."}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"Middleware","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/popguidesdk\/apiclient\/middleware","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Middleware","kind":"identifier"}]}}}